snippet.title: Quake: The Altar of Storms - ne_ruins - Full Playthrough - 1080p 60fps
snippet.description:
Playthrough of this really beautiful map created by necros. It features a completely new textureset, new enemies, bosses and a quad shotgun. Source port used is Fitzquake.

Addon: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/ne_ruins.html
Port: http://www.celephais.net/fitzquake/
